Despite being in his 18th season in the NBA and turning 38 years old in May 2023, Carmelo Anthony is still an active player. He is currently a member of the Los Angeles Lakers, where he signed a one-year deal for the 2021-2022 NBA season. Anthony has been able to stay in the league for so long due to his exceptional basketball skills and his ability to adapt his game to fit the changing dynamics of the sport.